{"type":"message","id":"057bf563","parentId":"355af9ff","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:42:57.908Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，自检结果：\n- 管管进化心跳：状态 ok\n- Guan-guan Heartbeat：状态 error，连续错误 1 次\n- 小艺进化心跳：状态 ok\n\n有一个error任务需要处理：\"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 10min\" 有 1 次连续错误。根据规则，需要清理连续3次error以上的任务。现在只有1次，还不到清理阈值。\n\n现在进入 2.2 修复阶段。我需要：\n- 用学到的\"SWE-bench评估技巧\"优化配置\n- 重点：用新知识优化进化系统本身\n\n从SWE-bench学到的主要观点是：评估重点从\"输出质量\"转向\"问题解决能力\"。\n\n让我思考如何应用到进化系统：\n1. 修改评估维度 - 关注问题解决而非任务执行\n2. 添加\"结果验证\"维度\n\n让我先检查版本号，然后记录版本。","thinkingSignature":"b817d14e9499a14587c0b8af3f077e0e30d70444114ecfafdd57d048d60d6565"},{"type":"text","text":"自检完成：\n- ✅ 管管进化心跳：ok\n- ⚠️ Guan-guan Heartbeat：error（连续1次，未达清理阈值）\n- ✅ 小艺进化心跳：ok\n\n### 2.2 修复 & 2.3 版本记录\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b8j4kfxcwkmf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\guan-guan\\workspace && uv run python evolution_archive/evolution_version.py history","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7161,"output":301,"cacheRead":36614,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44076,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773855767681}}
